@Comment:	the letter is to Chi's substitute teacher , who after two months is leaving (MOT's idea who to write to). Chi is very focused on activity and mouths words slightly as he writes. The text is his idea. Mot is watching from a few feet away. She makes eye contact with Chi as well as nods and shakes her head. After Chi writes a good time , he looks up and smiles at Mot as is finished. During love , Chi , Sis comes over to watch.
@Comment:	Dear Miss Sevingney I am going to miss you. I hope you have a good time. Love Chi [= full name].
